{"tid":2500727,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】埋葬地下2000年 土耳其羅馬劇場下出土50幾具陶俑","createTime":"2021-04-23T01:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T04:46:50.000Z","uid":219244,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3d39a07ed70a988570d53ebbf32f58660c95668d","tid":2500727,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYTKKR9AdNoPQRuRVPEyW6ADnfLYwkSdNDxQNKxjKdKEX?filename=ayhHJ8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FayhHJ8p.jpg&h=8bf92a84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><em>(所有圖都有唔錯嘅解像度，可以放大睇)</em></span><br />\n<br />\n土耳其考古學家研究古鎮米拉（Myra）的廢墟後，發現了50多個有2000-2200年歷史，捏塑成神祇、人和動物的陶俑。<br />\n<br />\n該團隊代表阿克德尼茲大學（Akdeniz University）和土耳其文化和旅遊部，在去年夏天挖掘了該鎮12,000個座位的羅馬時代劇院和一個位於其下層，更舊、更小的劇院。他們在較古老的結構中發現了小雕像，該結構可追溯到希臘化時期。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">*希臘化時期由公元前323年亞歷山大大帝逝世開始，到公元前31年左右羅馬帝國崛起結束</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcV64qh41PH7kSr3eJfQY6iA7P9qQoSQdNh18LjCd6L24?filename=OKbpXtq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOKbpXtq.jpg&h=45eabcd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ57Bwtynd2DT9sd77ydMoe4B8WHKStyEJ7mt6Htxj5aj?filename=bW8zzMK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbW8zzMK.png&h=8580a35c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n挖掘負責人考古學家Nevzat &Ccedil;evik形容這項藝術發現是「意想不到的大驚喜」。<br />\n<br />\n他補充說「彷彿古老的米拉人復活，一起穿越時光隧道來到了今天。」<br />\n<br />\n這些雕像的身高僅幾英寸，包括公羊、騎馬人像、婦女和孩童，還有一個載有水果的男孩，以及神話人物，如勒托（Leto）、阿緹蜜絲（Artemis）、阿波羅（Apollo）和海克力斯（Heracles）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">*泰坦勒托係鹹濕佬宙斯嘅伴侶，亦都係孿生姊弟月亮及狩獵女神阿緹蜜絲、太陽神阿波羅嘅老母</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmewLBnB7aauZckdK66Rxcu5NC38pHxw8X3HtNzH24wPtw?filename=NJSAjeZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJSAjeZ.jpg&h=10ba10ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfUkrPMc3rfmYheXkCJzXZVxcgCmEi91xGFyK8PUG3u4i?filename=1KVx5UW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1KVx5UW.jpg&h=4778c4d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfBZK1cP7DUU35syZefim3B3p65e1uV1kBnbV3ky6JZGR?filename=wYpbB1D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwYpbB1D.jpg&h=7623f1d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&Ccedil;evikqa指其中一些塑像仍然帶有紅色，藍色和粉紅色顏料的痕跡。<br />\n<br />\n他說「它們身上的染料得到部份保留，向我們展示了他們當時所穿衣服的顏色。」<br />\n<br />\n除陶俑外，研究小組還發現了散佈在希臘化劇院附近的陶瓷，青銅，鉛和銀器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYFJMKpX9qosBUs5tJMN3eWGboWS85kLF4EAB71BpfWHG?filename=QfCwCAZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQfCwCAZ.jpg&h=a9cafd29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">Source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/dozens-2000-year-old-terracotta-figurines-found-turkey-180976978/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smithsonianmag.com%2Fsmart-news%2Fdozens-2000-year-old-terracotta-figurines-found-turkey-180976978%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrbsYlYTGbxuQQGsxDmAgPG8%3D&h=e231c8cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/dozens-2000-year-old-terracotta-figurines-found-turkey-180976978/</a></span>"},{"pid":"742f734e0a91f3dddf1601058868e2c82b47f80f","tid":2500727,"uid":219244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeVoicRawjQVmqjUDJfLn6jnJMLDvWLxBu7cr9J67hrz8?filename=ZFaY1VW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFaY1VW.png&h=a9e90b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSSHGuSd7yS7s3MiaoKGSqHs1UCJRDMhtPryqokruaBGJ?filename=ox7P8AZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fox7P8AZ.jpg&h=012418c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmarWB7TAFUGCinC12j16QakDUB2ua2vC9seSAxTwAw7fH?filename=XNghx2H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNghx2H.jpg&h=af7bfaf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeMKXWyBXZsYEnhKoobps2mZr19Fp2ieT1r9WqLq6wSqw?filename=37N4XBd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37N4XBd.png&h=ca7929d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdqwC8hDfpRRJEByc2x9JmB5qWANnkxZHLg6UckHhmbAb?filename=1EoLG4k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1EoLG4k.png&h=baf67207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRY1XjDAoPttSoPxW4c59SAS35hzuZNegsVyGMpQr5z5K?filename=oDNkvXG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoDNkvXG.png&h=347cd4f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaGMSeyAt7kT9YwZTjv68kYTuSspsZGjaCz1yu9ncp3Zp?filename=2B8f39p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2B8f39p.jpg&h=c595d282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n米拉（Myra）位於現代土耳其南部海岸安德里亞庫斯河（Andriacus River）的河口附近，數千年來一直是地中海重要的港口城市，幾百年來一直受到不同地區強國的控制。根據《大不列顛百科全書》，它是古代沿海城邦聯盟呂西亞（Lycia）最重要的城鎮之一，該聯盟歷史可以追溯到公元前14世紀。在公元前6世紀，波斯軍隊征服了呂西亞，後來該地區在羅馬的控制下，於公元43年逐漸被吞併成為羅馬行省。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZLJwV7d3SXSqVDkhwbtmUcyz9zGAsCEZ1pPcPd9j1yU7?filename=g8BQSyo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8BQSyo.jpg&h=83547e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/c7/Myra_Tombs_Temples.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fc%2Fc7%2FMyra_Tombs_Temples.jpg&h=66ec98f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n米拉最著名的是於公元前5世紀至前3世紀期間在岩壁上開鑿的陵墓，它們看起來像是木製房屋和神龕。城內的羅馬劇場，建於公元三世紀，是安那托利亞（Anatolia）境內最令人印象深刻的劇場之一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4e/Myra_theatre.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F4%2F4e%2FMyra_theatre.jpg&h=a5adcb5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Hurriyet每日新聞》指，該地點的挖掘工作已經進行了十多年。整個夏天，項目負責人同數十名研究人員和工人在Demre進行調查和發掘。<br />\n<br />\n&Ccedil;evik說：「我可以說，我們今年夏天在米拉古城劇場進行的發掘給安那托利亞考古學提供了一年中最重要的禮物之一。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRyVU7G4AwAUw2PadBdGRVjeJV2Q25ex9UESTZrw3DX5d?filename=poxwCus.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpoxwCus.jpg&h=8e6b14c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPQktiHpTMvoYLaki7xyCp4op18sPtqr5dEDYsFkofYnH?filename=noF98A8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnoF98A8.png&h=2e7a93cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXenZee2te35HdiMn27EvxeduGFXKmCT6vPSq5vn5dGMJ?filename=pdTPo9v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdTPo9v.jpg&h=fe19ba61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfWYVMqkN8VTPfttRfQy9vobdA7Zh3tbGNPfEeuycY77r?filename=B8QKc9F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8QKc9F.png&h=d0893b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cevirigazetesi.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/11-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cevirigazetesi.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F11-2.jpg&h=b0e08850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdtBvUzkShcuxQLCpSUZxb49LDwGckoBi3qXaf251rvJX?filename=ofTS6nS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FofTS6nS.jpg&h=d5250cbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除許多完整的小陶俑外，《Live Science》還報告該團隊發現了50多個沒有屍體的頭部，這一發現表明更多的文物仍在等待發現。<br />\n<br />\n目前，該團隊正在繼續將剩餘的小雕像拼湊在一起。它計劃與Demre的呂西亞文明博物館（Museum of Lycian Civilizations）分享這些文物，然後將其展示給公眾。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4in8pqN4cPA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4in8pqN4cPA&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrbsYlYTGbxuQQGsxDmAgPG8%3D&h=ca03bcba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4in8pqN4cPA</a>"},{"pid":"2bc2cb8dcb854f7b0fcc7e57adc75977b2e1aec8","tid":2500727,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:18:41.000Z","msg":"抄兵馬俑？中國又可以話土耳其係自古以來的領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded042bd874d33d96cb37017411fcb6435478254","tid":2500727,"uid":113250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:20:51.000Z","msg":"50多個沒有屍體的頭部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17846cec6ebd5303a65a50f6a9baa01aa74ee57","tid":2500727,"uid":219244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T02:35:29.000Z","msg":"Anatolia仲有好多其他希臘&mdash;羅馬時期嘅遺跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼<br />\n好brief咁講一講呢一兩年土耳其仲有咩考古發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><blockquote>&lsquo;Be cheerful, live your life:&rsquo; Ancient Mosaic With Greek 「meme」found in Turkey&rsquo;s south</blockquote></em></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUFKj9UE4jp9NQm6WksFqYa4m8zsMDGeNgPUfoxYSmXKw?filename=sRKOGW0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRKOGW0.png&h=3c2235ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢幅有2,400年曆史嘅骷髏骨馬賽克係喺土耳其南部鄰近敘利亞邊境嘅Hatay省發現<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTj4CGiEDyY2qfrgi8qriAqsVZUGXLBNg7DiKa9zioPU2?filename=v5hsXvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv5hsXvm.jpg&h=764ff59a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面寫住<em>Be cheerful, enjoy your life</em>(快樂吧，來享受生命)￼(地獄meme?)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWo9Pt8qcmKFhcPYjcegx6N6LGUtddDQquaWZV37R4Up1?filename=WiEV6oG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWiEV6oG.png&h=1e27ad54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬賽克位於一間羅馬(希臘？)式別墅嘅飯廳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><em>2,400-year-old mask of Dionysus unearthed in western Turkey</em></strong></blockquote><br />\n呢副有2400年歷史嘅Dionysus面具係土耳西部嘅Daskyleion街城出土，Dionysus係古希臘嘅酒神同狂歡之神<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQyzkdAN8bjEVUHxYiQzgZrvYsxeeuaamYwKH29jU9UJx?filename=b0dLKxX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0dLKxX.jpg&h=6390bbc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個可能是係一個奉獻品，Dionysus嘅信徒會係獻祭或者儀式舉行時，戴上面具，釋放內心嘅慾望同情緒(即刻發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><blockquote>Ordu unearthed the 2,100-year-old the Kybele Statue, and 2,000 historical artifacts</blockquote></em></strong><br />\n呢啲係Ordu省Kurul Castle出土嘅Dionysus同Pan(潘，牧神)陶俑係宗教用具，啲人會係儀式入邊故意打爛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW6VitH82bT8aB1Rg7YX3Wpk7YjiX5xdKX9mXGg62Yxk9?filename=KR3WRtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKR3WRtB.jpg&h=7bcdd791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQaxYvDxA4qntkyvbPq2VvZKnsszq3LvanmBeyR56JJeC?filename=oTzGh8C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoTzGh8C.jpg&h=87015459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmScE5T6DxSrYoTZQ1a1jvr9p9EyFnH9QwNMMkYq6AN3AA?filename=ZNMdTGY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNMdTGY.png&h=94d0c36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW5SFVy2ynpSNgCmQF81n7aRBctayBKhfwqgZwuz5k12q?filename=r71mh8D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr71mh8D.png&h=b7ea6b54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPeQ5rHoBKfFPDU1G4UxkE4ThPWAXxPyv2VKUmBY5r85C?filename=YSkBRtK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSkBRtK.png&h=a683a19b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRykq8uADbAvhjbzGcrotxos11K5EtvwST3ookN4uCJut?filename=MLKV615.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLKV615.png&h=b9276c52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n較早前一座高1米嘅地母神Cybele雕像被發現時極罕有仲係神龕原位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVx8XiaNVRM469EG3D7gqCntcbHfo48eNKrb89ZGrQnE4?filename=y1JS9fB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy1JS9fB.jpg&h=2047bc8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmeur7cQv58edeVgJ3TG1f1XhAWB5LP2schjZesDCtdZrG?filename=4JqqKOW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4JqqKOW.png&h=a55a0a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><blockquote>Marble Blocks Carved With Theatrical Masks Unearthed In Ancient City Of Stratonikeia</blockquote></em></strong><br />\n考古學家係位於土耳其南部Mugla省嘅古城Stratonikeia中發現以下有2200年歷史嘅鬼臉<br />\n<br />\n呢啲刻係大理石上嘅鬼臉埋係羅馬劇場近舞台位置嘅地下，可能係劇場嘅裝飾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/crystalball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ4KrN2xEW6YyDszcChhPMoncdSZTNaKBzxMm77EG36fE?filename=WU3zCPa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWU3zCPa.jpg&h=6779e294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZPtXfSAmKjwrXXQ1c5jSUjnDdNDd15HffYaG6Jfko1Fs?filename=6o65Kt6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6o65Kt6.jpg&h=05b7f47f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVgq1sMm4QT2ZzgSjJJeH2niVkCwa3mNDgEXbxmSv5guJ?filename=F8aij3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8aij3Q.jpg&h=612425f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdZcVmZFfMRyokeKVxAKr2LntMPhygSG83fbLfPiXhrJp?filename=Ce8PrHr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCe8PrHr.jpg&h=68a2f036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcXRxjNyWFRuX2XzLPYMepEmRfxWiGKfCcP4HsxVhNWm8?filename=UAEnMHs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUAEnMHs.jpg&h=10be9fa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdw3DzrNmgzkrE544RKY6jswi9MqSo1G8A6Y5sMS4WPyL?filename=bbKOHfN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbKOHfN.jpg&h=cce0013b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYABF2SN6JMKmyWxHujKxJEY7pBmzCi8WE4ufcTrsUU6Z?filename=nXe3v88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnXe3v88.jpg&h=789e63b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc3co1TRXVpwKUnHEGmQAEyWZgkPKgJzujwmEqbebLbfQ?filename=BnV6tVO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnV6tVO.jpg&h=1cb2e286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVyeh9VGVL6sS428K6iiq35jLWhSwMd818ctAu7epBe1v?filename=HdCMtVP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHdCMtVP.jpg&h=18f932e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfGNbyDgmARhBgPEzaWMqcNceDVUxEMGtD9UYm1pSxEwJ?filename=qoAVnfP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoAVnfP.jpg&h=85e13a53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmey8vW1MN9TGACPxmHj8CrXmzfT4J8mQjXoNMsqKJ17dQ?filename=kxrNdoR.jpg\" data-thum