1:04.000Z","msg":"項少龍去過土耳其<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad678abc942c6a457cec52a3388516464163a83","tid":2500727,"uid":219244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:41:56.000Z","msg":"上面啲finding雖然唔係咩大發現，啲陶俑都係好普通貨<br />\n但就可以反映到當時人嘅日常生活同文化習俗<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都中意古希臘、古羅馬呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順便share埋之前另一個【考古】po：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">【多圖】埃及重大考古發現　3000年歷史近乎完整「失落黃金城」重現<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2484490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2484490</a></span>"},{"pid":"9d38ba7a3e2cb07cd76e720747f9051478c94b27","tid":2500727,"uid":106798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:44:46.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9dd7f1b6c139db96c5f8329559efcafa830347ff","tid":2500727,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:46:50.000Z","msg":"今日俾啲回化突厥人侵佔"}],"pinned":{"pid":"c17846cec6ebd5303a65a50f6a9baa01aa74ee57","tid":2500727,"uid":219244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T02:35:29.000Z","msg":"Anatolia仲有好多其他希臘&mdash;羅馬時期嘅遺跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼<br />\n好brief咁講一講呢一兩年土耳其仲有咩考古發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><blockquote>&lsquo;Be cheerful, live your life:&rsquo; Ancient Mosaic With Greek 「meme」found in Turkey&rsquo;s south</blockquote></em></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRKOGW0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRKOGW0.png&h=3c2235ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢幅有2,400年曆史嘅骷髏骨馬賽克係喺土耳其南部鄰近敘利亞邊境嘅Hatay省發現<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v5hsXvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv5hsXvm.jpg&h=764ff59a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面寫住<em>Be cheerful, enjoy your life</em>(快樂吧，來享受生命)￼(地獄meme?)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WiEV6oG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWiEV6oG.png&h=1e27ad54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬賽克位於一間羅馬(希臘？)式別墅嘅飯廳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><em>2,400-year-old mask of Dionysus unearthed in western Turkey</em></strong></blockquote><br />\n呢副有2400年歷史嘅Dionysus面具係土耳西部嘅Daskyleion街城出土，Dionysus係古希臘嘅酒神同狂歡之神<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b0dLKxX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0dLKxX.jpg&h=6390bbc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個可能是係一個奉獻品，Dionysus嘅信徒會係獻祭或者儀式舉行時，戴上面具，釋放內心嘅慾望同情緒(即刻發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><blockquote>Ordu unearthed the 2,100-year-old the Kybele Statue, and 2,000 historical artifacts</blockquote></em></strong><br />\n呢啲係Ordu省Kurul Castle出土嘅Dionysus同Pan(潘，牧神)陶俑係宗教用具，啲人會係儀式入邊故意打爛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KR3WRtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKR3WRtB.jpg&h=7bcdd791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oTzGh8C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoTzGh8C.jpg&h=87015459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNMdTGY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNMdTGY.png&h=94d0c36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r71mh8D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr71mh8D.png&h=b7ea6b54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSkBRtK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSkBRtK.png&h=a683a19b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLKV615.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLKV615.png&h=b9276c52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n較早前一座高1米嘅地母神Cybele雕像被發現時極罕有仲係神龕原位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y1JS9fB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy1JS9fB.jpg&h=2047bc8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4JqqKOW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4JqqKOW.png&h=a55a0a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><blockquote>Marble Blocks Carved With Theatrical Masks Unearthed In Ancient City Of Stratonikeia</blockquote></em></strong><br />\n考古學家係位於土耳其南部Mugla省嘅古城Stratonikeia中發現以下有2200年歷史嘅鬼臉<br />\n<br />\n呢啲刻係大理石上嘅鬼臉埋係羅馬劇場近舞台位置嘅地下，可能係劇場嘅裝飾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/crystalball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WU3zCPa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWU3zCPa.jpg&h=6779e294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6o65Kt6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6o65Kt6.jpg&h=05b7f47f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8aij3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8aij3Q.jpg&h=612425f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ce8PrHr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCe8PrHr.jpg&h=68a2f036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UAEnMHs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUAEnMHs.jpg&h=10be9fa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbKOHfN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbKOHfN.jpg&h=cce0013b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nXe3v88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnXe3v88.jpg&h=789e63b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnV6tVO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnV6tVO.jpg&h=1cb2e286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HdCMtVP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHdCMtVP.jpg&h=18f932e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoAVnfP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoAVnfP.jpg&h=85e13a53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kxrNdoR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkxrNdoR.jpg&h=76369cb3&s={SIZE}\" />"}}